title: Port Official Talks Cyber Security on Capitol Hill (The Port of Long Beach)
text: ( Source : The Port of Long Beach ) Federal officials should forge a comprehensive strategy to defend the nation's ports from cyber attacks, Port of Long Beach Director of Security Services Randy Parsons told a U.S. House of Representatives
